      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="A pre-established cut-off period would be determined (either daily, weekly or monthly).  Sub-ledger/sub-system feeds would be received for the period end final transactions and the sub-ledger/sub-system periods would be closed to ensure that no further transactions are processed for that period.  A reconciliation should then be performed to ensure accuracy of the data."/>
