      <textAnnotation id="sid-9FAC43CA-C9DF-470C-B0ED-C6DFC722D26A" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Reclassification of GL Accounts for retained earnings and dividend will be performed through custom program (FPRE0360_CFIN)</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-5EAD2F66-D7E3-4A13-918A-6605658223D2" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Subledger Closings, reporting, accruals process will continue in ECC as part of R1 and the same will be replicated in S4 through CFIN replication</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-F51911E3-9213-45E3-9A58-3868349E27A6" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
